org.cpsolver.studentsct.report

Class RequestGroupTable

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.cpsolver.studentsct.report.AbstractStudentSectioningReport
      • org.cpsolver.studentsct.report.RequestGroupTable
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    StudentSectioningReport, StudentSectioningReport.Filter

    public class RequestGroupTable
extends AbstractStudentSectioningReport
    This reports lists all request groups (including course name and group name) and the current spreads. For each group, the current average spread (see RequestGroup.getAverageSpread(Assignment)) is listed together with all the classes that the students of the group are enrolled into and their spreads (see RequestGroup.getSectionSpread(Assignment, Section)).

    The average spread corresponds with the probability of two students of the group to attend the same section. The section spread is a break down of the average spread by each section.
